00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:14.560
Je refuse !

00:15:14.690 --> 00:15:18.150
Pourquoi ?! On a voyagé ensemble !

00:15:18.730 --> 00:15:19.940
Luffy-dono !

00:15:20.070 --> 00:15:21.190
Je refuse !

00:15:21.290 --> 00:15:23.040
